{"tid":439894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【慎入】花780萬全身整容 變性人造人：我已最接近完美","createTime":"2017-10-18T08:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T09:03:15.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6157f6f17720ee95fa4254a867b5e37308da38a3","tid":439894,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171017/large/1508219446_d40f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171017%2Flarge%2F1508219446_d40f.jpg&h=eec27923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國新澤西州一位變性人花了100萬美元（約780萬港元）全身整容，希望把本來男兒身的自己變成芭比，她說：「我感到我已最接近完美。」<br />\n<br />\n35歲的托爾斯（Jason Torres）自4歲起就想當芭比，她說自有記憶以來，就覺得自己是被困男兒身的女兒心。如今為自己改名「Nikki Exotika」的托爾斯說：「以前去洗手間時我總是坐下來，我從不站起。即使在那個年紀，我都覺得自己帶着錯的生殖器官出生。」年輕的托爾斯感到困惑又羞恥，只能將秘密埋藏心底。<br />\n<br />\n在學校托爾斯飽受欺凌，放學後她化上妝、換上熱褲到同道中人的酒吧，首次認識到其他跨性別人士。她19歲開始服食非法荷爾蒙，並接受變性手術，為追求完美的芭比形象，托爾斯多年來總共花費100萬美元，在眼、鼻、胸、臀、髮線等全身多處動刀。<br />\n<br />\n伊人說：「一切都值得。因為我到全球各處時，大家都看著我說：『哇，看看她的身體，她看來似芭比一樣。』總是想與我拍照。」她續道：「我正實現我的夢想。」<br />\n<br />\n托爾斯即將在電視真人騷「Plastics of Hollywood」粉墨登場，她下個心願就是買架粉紅色寶馬，再找個夢中男神一同出遊。她說：「我在找一個高大、非常火辣的肌肉男。我愛紋身及看來似Ken（芭比男友）的美麗男孩。」<br />\n真人騷內還包括其餘11位「改造人」，該節目經理指，托爾斯可能比其他人經歷過更多手術，同時也更堅強，「我知道很多人曾在學校被欺凌而要服抗抑鬱藥，但她繼續夢想變成她想要的樣子」。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約郵報》 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/164115_1ee6f969fecff57eaa33161017810a38.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2F164115_1ee6f969fecff57eaa33161017810a38.PNG&h=03c56b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/164115_c8052bee9d894293bc27c70e4ca61a03.PNG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2F164115_c8052bee9d894293bc27c70e4ca61a03.PNG&d=3l%2FqZyfP6LRDkR2YTTFA08n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=8b32aa62\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/164115_c8052bee9d894293bc27c70e4ca61a03.PNG</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20171018/57341517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20171018%2F57341517&d=3l%2FqZyfP6LRDkR2YTTFA08n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=a7bbfa0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20171018%2F57341517&h=4a2d4628\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20171018/57341517</a>"},{"pid":"44050e2523c2436418dde1d8f9cfb4dcd043cb1e","tid":439894,"uid":17081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2016/03/04/b/b02c97183da4246b83bd40db31a1a0ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2016%2F03%2F04%2Fb%2Fb02c97183da4246b83bd40db31a1a0ed.jpg&h=902423d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1645681cee90ea4dcbed30795d521b4b8b0280fd","tid":439894,"uid":137829,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:52:38.000Z","msg":"都係咪俾啲細路玩咁多芭比..."},{"pid":"00d598581f8debb1ae3aa672cb50494a1972b245","tid":439894,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e34a792c9de162d5bf5079caf9e477f25485636e","tid":439894,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:55:17.000Z","msg":"有啲恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a4c2a7aee2f6557a3a6f54caffc62eab7f3308","tid":439894,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以加咗慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b0307ab2d